  "response": "Shah Rukh Khan has received numerous international awards and recognitions throughout his career. Here are some of the most notable ones:\n\n**Film Awards:**\n\n*   **Filmfare Awards:** Though these are primarily Indian awards, their prestige is recognized internationally. Shah Rukh Khan has won 14 Filmfare Awards, including eight for Best Actor.\n\n*   **Zee Cine Awards:** Similar to Filmfare, these Indian awards hold international recognition, and Shah Rukh Khan has won several, including Best Actor awards.\n\n*   **Asian Film Awards:** Shah Rukh Khan has received nominations at the Asian Film Awards.\n\n**National Honors and Cultural Awards:**\n\n*   **Padma Shri (India):** This is one of India's highest civilian honors, awarded in 2005 for his contributions to Indian cinema.\n\n*   **Ordre des Arts et des Lettres (France):** He was awarded this prestigious French honor in 2007, recognizing his contribution to the arts.\n\n*   **Chevalier L\u00e9gion d'Honneur (France):** In 2014, he was awarded the Knight of the Legion of Honour, France's highest civilian honor, for his exceptional career and contribution to cinema.\n\n*   **World Economic Forum's Crystal Award:** He received this award in 2018 for his leadership in championing children's and women's rights in India.\n\n**Other Recognitions:**\n\n*   **Doctorate from the University of Edinburgh (UK):** He received an honorary doctorate in 2015 for his outstanding record of philanthropy, altruism, and humanitarian endeavors, and for his global reach as an actor.\n\n*   **Doctorate from Maulana Azad National Urdu University (India):** He received an honorary doctorate in 2016 for his contribution to the promotion of Urdu language and culture.\n\n*   **Doctorate from La Trobe University (Australia):** He received an honorary doctorate in 2019 for his contributions to Indian cinema and his humanitarian work.\n\n*   **Recognitions from International Film Festivals:** While not necessarily awards, he's been a guest of honor and recognized at major film festivals like the Berlin International Film Festival and the Cannes Film Festival, which signifies international recognition.\n\n*   **Global Icon Awards:** Numerous organizations worldwide have recognized him as a global icon due to his widespread popularity and influence.\n\nThis list is not exhaustive, but it highlights some of the most significant international awards and honors Shah Rukh Khan has received, demonstrating his global impact beyond Bollywood.",
